* OSSIM-0.9.6 (01 Jul 2004)

    01 Jul 2004 FOT <fot@ossim.net> :
    * Many server bugfixes.
    * Directive groups.
    * New correlation tag: sticky_different.

    28 Jun 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * A lot of framework bugfixes (thanks to Stéphane Fournier)
    * Alarm summaries at alarm console.

    24 Jun 2004 DK <dk@ossim.net> :
    * Many, many bugfixes (:p).

    23 Jun 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net>:
    * Agent: Monitors reimplemented.
      New protected list (MonitorList) to store monitor objects instead of
      creating monitor threads for each watch-rule received.

    21 Jun 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * scripts/control_panel.py: 
      - suppressed unnecessary insert querys (faster control panel, 
        smaller tables).
      - verbose mode (-v --verbose)
    * agent/Agent.inc: reconnect code bugfixes and improvements.
    * scripts/acid_cache.pl: better error control.

    18 Jun 2004 DK <dk@ossim.net> :
    * 0.9.5p2 released

