    23 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * agent/agent: 
      - daemon mode (-d, --daemon)
      - log debug and error messages to '/var/log/ossim/agent.log' and 
        '/var/log/ossim/agent_error.log' respectively.
      - quite mode by default (-v to show debug messages)

    22 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * agent/MonitorNtopSession.py: Ntop-3 session date format adjust.
    * www/rrd_conf/*: Insert/Modify rrd settings in the new rrd_config table.

    21 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * agent/Monitor.py: 
      - Captured exception when monitor creates excessive
        threads, causing server blocking.
      - Lock web requests to ntop with a mutex to avoid it crash when more
        than one request is made.

    20 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * agent/MonitorNtopHostinfo.py, agent/MonitorNtopSession.py: 
      serious bugfixes.
    * agent/Agent.py, agent/ParserP0f.py, agent/ParserArpwatch.py: 
      new method to send notifications like OS and Mac changes.
    * agent/Config.py: 
      attribute 'name' changed to 'process'.
    * agent/Config.py, agent/MonitorWatchdog.py: 
      watchdog interval configuration via config.xml.

    15 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * include/classes/RRD_config.inc, www/rrd_conf/*: 
      new rrd_config table (substitute of rrd_conf and rrd_conf_global tables)

    14 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * agent/ParserP0f.py: important bug fixed. ParserP0f did not save OS
      information correctly and sent numerous and repeated alerts.
    * db/create_mysql.sql: new rrd_config table (substitute of rrd_conf and
      rrd_conf_global tables).
    * db/ossim_data.sql: new ntop sids.
    * include/classes/Host_mac.inc, include/classes/Host_os.inc,
      www/control_panel/mac.php, www/control_panel/os.php,.
      www/control_panel/anomalies.php: many bugfixes related to date formats.

    13 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * db/ossim_data.sql: priority and reliability tunning (snort)

    07 Apr 2004 David Gil <dgil@ossim.net> :
    * www/conf/pluginupdate.php: plugin's priority & reliability can be 0
    * www/control_panel/mac.php, www/control_panel/os.php: 
      Important bug fixed regarding mysql 3.X compatibility. 
      Thanks to Jordi Figueras <jfigueras at semic.es>

    05 Apr 2004 David Gil: <dgil@ossim.net> :
